{'id': '20126', 'school_id': '3419', 'type': '69000', 'content': '<p style="text-indent: 32px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">承德应用技术职业学院是</span>2018年5月经河北省人民政府批准</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">教育部正式备案成立的一所公办全日制高等职业院校。学</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">院</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">坐落</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">于</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">驰名中外、风光秀美的历史文化名城河北省承德市</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">凤凰山脚下，环境优美，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">占地</span>446.38亩，建筑面积13.19万平方米，学校总投资10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">.9</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">亿元</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">其中，先进的配套实训设备、附属设施投资</span>2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">.2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">亿元，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一期办学规模</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">6000人</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">院立足承德、服务京津冀</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，重点建设</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">面向</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二三产业专业群，培养适应承德市及京津冀区域经济结构调整、产业转型升级和创新驱动发展战略需要的生产服务一线紧缺的应用型、复合型技术技能人才。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学院设有智能制造、电子信息、</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">现代服务</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、交通运输、学前教育</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、艺术设计</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">个系，</span>23个专业。现有在校生1700余人，2020年继续面向全国招生。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学院</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">制定了</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">“</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">13510</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">”</span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发展规划和三基地、三示范的建设目标，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">未来</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">将</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">把</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">院</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">建设成为服务承德及京津冀经济社会发展的高质量的应用技术人才培养基地</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">促进就业</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">助力技术技能人才终身发展的一流职业培训基地</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">直接服务二三产业转型升级发展、产教学研训一体的创新创业及实用技术研发基地。努力把学院办成全国教育扶贫的示范、京津冀协同教育协同发展的示范和中高衔接一体发展的示范。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">学院依托天津中德应用技术大学指导办学，</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">以</span>“校企合作、国际合作、从严治校、双创育人”为支柱，秉承“厚德励能、成才报国”校训，发扬“艰苦创业、勤奋进取、勇于担当、追求卓越”的学院精神，以“精道艺、重知行”为学生发展目标，为新时代中国特色社会主义事业培养高素质应用型人才，为青年学子实现技能成才、技术报国的理想助力。</span></p><p><br/></p>', 'status': '1', 'update_time': '2020-03-12 16:23:24', 'type_name': '学校概况'}